From 8ccae9039f62194924c64b30fdf92b7adda47d06 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Mar 2026 02:55:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add Prometheus metrics generation (schema v1)

Generate static Prometheus exposition format file at /metrics with:
- Exit DNS Health: per-relay failure status, latency, consecutive failures
- AROI Monitoring: per-relay validation status for configured relays
- Meta: build info, generation timestamp, source availability
- Info metrics: human-readable relay metadata (non-ABI)

Prefix: aeo1_ (valid Prometheus name, cannot start with digit)
Atomic write: metrics.tmp -> os.rename -> metrics
Deterministic output: sorted by fingerprint
Schema v1 contract with frozen label sets

Files:
- allium/lib/prometheus_metrics.py: ~300 line generator module
- allium/lib/site_generator.py: integration hook after search index
- allium/allium.py: progress step count update (+2)
- tests/unit/test_prometheus_metrics.py: 42 unit tests
